-- LG Dental - English-Speaking Dental Clinic in San Pedro del Pinatar, Murcia
('LG Dental', 'Dentists', 'Established English-speaking dental clinic founded in 2005 by Dr. Luis Miguel Sánchez Suárez, serving the San Pedro del Pinatar and Murcia community for over 10 years. Specialized in dental implants, oral surgery, cosmetic dentistry, orthodontics, endodontics, periodontics, and prosthodontics. State-of-the-art facilities equipped with the latest technology including intraoral cameras, computer-aided prosthesis design, endodontic apex locators, and computer-guided implant surgery. Committed to providing the highest quality standards in dental care with a patient-centered approach. Full English-speaking staff experienced in treating international patients and expats. Monday to Friday: 9am-1pm and 4pm-8pm.', 'Av. Las Salinas, 49', 'San Pedro del Pinatar', 'Murcia', '+34 968 186 660', 'info@lgdental.es', 'https://www.lgdental.es/en/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
